40 INSTRUCTIONS RISC-V


Group 1- Control Transfer Instructions

1) JAL - Jump and Link 
2) JALR - Jump and Link Register 
3) BEQ - Branch if Equal
4) BNE - Branch if not Equal 
5) BLT - Branch Less Than 
6) BLTU - Branch if Less Than Unsigned 
7) BGE - Branch if Greater Than Equal 
8) BGEU - Branch if Greater Than Equal Unsigned
9) BGT - Branch if Greater Than
10) BGTU - Branch if Greater Than Unsigned 
11) BLE - Branch if Less Than Equal
12) BLEU - Branch if Less Than Equal Unsigned

J RA    801F0793

Group 2- Load Instructions

OPCODE = 0000011	

1) LB   - Load Byte				FUNCTION = 000
2) LH   - Load Halfword			FUNCTION = 001	
3) LW  - Load Word				FUNCTION = 010
4) LBU - Load Byte Unsigned		FUNCTION = 100
5) LHU - Load Hafword Unsigned		FUNCTION = 101
	
Group 3 Store Instruction 

OPCODE = 0100011

1) SB - Store Byte				FUNCTION = 000
2) SH - Store Halfword			FUNCTION = 001
3) SW - Store Word 			FUNCTION = 010


Group 4  U-TYPE

1) LUI - Load Upper Immediate	  OPCODE= 0110111   
2) AUIPC - Add Upper Immediate  OPCODE= 0010111
                  to Program Counter


Group 5- Register Immediate Instruction

OPCODE = 0010011

FUNCTION
1) ADDI - Add Immediate			FUNCTION=000
2) SLTI - Set Less Than Immediate	FUNCTION=010
3) SLTIU - Set Less Than			FUNCTION=011
                 Immediate Unsigned
4) XORI - Xor Immediate			FUNCTION=100
5) ORI - OR Immediate			FUNCTION=110
6) ANDI - AND Immediate			FUNCTION=111
7) SLLI - Shift Logical Left Immediate	FUNCTION=0000000 001
8) SRLI - Shift Right Left Immediate	FUNCTION=0000000 101
9) SRAI - Shift Right Arithmetic		FUNCTION=0100000 101
		       Immediate


Group 6- Register Register Instructions

OPCODE = 0110011

FUNCTION
1) ADD - Add  				FUNTION=  0000000  000 
2) SUB - Sub  				FUNTION=  0100000  000
3) SLL - Shift Logical Left			FUNTION=  0000000  001
4) SLT - Set Less Than			FUNTION=  0000000  010
5) SLTU - Set Less Than Unsigned	FUNTION=  0000000  011
6) XOR - Xor					FUNTION=  0000000  100
7) SRL - Shift Right Logical		FUNTION=  0000000  101
8) SRA - Shift Right Arithmetic		FUNTION=  0100000  101
9) OR - Or 					FUNTION=  0000000  110
10) AND - And				FUNTION=  0000000  111
